00:39:44.220 --> 00:39:48.480 align:middle line:84%
And I said, so
where do I belong?

00:39:48.480 --> 00:39:52.030 align:middle line:90%
And they said, "in the center."

00:39:52.030 --> 00:39:55.140 align:middle line:10%
So I started to walk to
the center of the stones,

00:39:55.140 --> 00:40:00.420 align:middle line:10%
and I got to the middle of
it, and suddenly, I kind of

00:40:00.420 --> 00:40:03.970 align:middle line:10%
accepted that I had
to be in the center.

00:40:03.970 --> 00:40:06.420 align:middle line:90%
So I am the center.

