but the team is to surround you.

00:40:23.280 --> 00:40:27.510 align:middle line:84%
The team is to hold
everything to be a sphere.

00:40:27.510 --> 00:40:29.820 align:middle line:90%
And you mark the center.

00:40:29.820 --> 00:40:31.350 align:middle line:90%
Where do we go?

00:40:31.350 --> 00:40:32.220 align:middle line:90%
I am."

00:40:32.220 --> 00:40:35.050 align:middle line:90%


