When I said this,
something in me

00:40:38.170 --> 00:40:40.900 align:middle line:84%
started to see every
one of my lives

00:40:40.900 --> 00:40:44.140 align:middle line:84%
and every one of the stones
became each one of me,

00:40:44.140 --> 00:40:46.570 align:middle line:90%
of myself, staring at me.

00:40:46.570 --> 00:40:47.560 align:middle line:90%
Not other people.

00:40:47.560 --> 00:40:51.250 align:middle line:90%
It was just my soul watching me.

00:40:51.250 --> 00:40:54.730 align:middle line:84%
And every stone was
one of my lives.

00:40:54.730 --> 00:40:58.750 align:middle line:90%
And I saw all of them.

00:40:58.750 --> 00:41:02.920 align:middle line:84%
And they started to come to
me and becoming me and saying,

00:41:02.920 --> 00:41:06.520 align:middle line:84%
"We are the circle
that holds who you are.

00:41:06.520 --> 00:41:10.300 align:middle line:84%
So don't expect for others
to be in that circle.

00:41:10.300 --> 00:41:15.230 align:middle line:84%
We are that circle that
puts you in the center."

00:41:15.230 --> 00:41:18.460 align:middle line:84%
So it was very
healing, that moment,

00:41:18.460 --> 00:41:24.760 align:middle line:84%
in which my soul kind of let
itself die from all the weight

00:41:24.760 --> 00:41:29.620 align:middle line:84%
that it was waiting for being
in the center for other people.

00:41:29.620 --> 00:41:33.100 align:middle line:84%
Like, the responsibility
of being seen by others,

00:41:33.100 --> 00:41:37.030 align:middle line:84%
but they said the only
ones from which you

00:41:37.030 --> 00:41:40.330 align:middle line:84%
have to feel that
you are being seen

00:41:40.330 --> 00:41:44.530 align:middle line:84%
is ourselves, which is yourself
in different timelines.

00:41:44.530 --> 00:41:47.680 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Freddy, it sounds like
he had some kind of epiphany

00:41:47.680 --> 00:41:49.490 align:middle line:90%
with the stones, too.

00:41:49.490 --> 00:41:52.090 align:middle line:84%
>>SILVA: The good thing about
these very out of the way

00:41:52.090 --> 00:41:53.950 align:middle line:84%
places, which take
effort to get their,

00:41:53.950 --> 00:41:56.680 align:middle line:84%
cost of fortune to fly there,
and then you get bad weather

00:41:56.680 --> 00:41:59.650 align:middle line:84%
when you get there, is
the fact that-- and this

00:41:59.650 --> 00:42:02.620 align:middle line:84%
is very specific, not just of
Orkney, but even more specific

00:42:02.620 --> 00:42:04.653 align:middle line:84%
of the Isle of Lewis
where we have some stone

00:42:04.653 --> 00:42:06.820 align:middle line:84%
circles, which, unless you
know how to read the map,

00:42:06.820 --> 00:42:07.787 align:middle line:90%
you won't find them.

00:42:07.787 --> 00:42:09.370 align:middle line:84%
And they're some of
my favorite places

00:42:09.370 --> 00:42:13.210 align:middle line:84%
because they've been totally
unaffected by war, human folly

00:42:13.210 --> 00:42:14.780 align:middle line:90%
of any other kind of problem.

00:42:14.780 --> 00:42:16.548 align:middle line:84%
So if the stones
remember everything--

00:42:16.548 --> 00:42:17.590 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Almost pristine.

00:42:17.590 --> 00:42:18.910 align:middle line:84%
>>SILVA: You just
go to these places

00:42:18.910 --> 00:42:20.618 align:middle line:84%
and it's like you're
meeting your family.

00:42:20.618 --> 00:42:22.180 align:middle line:84%
I mean, I can't
even tell you how--

00:42:22.180 --> 00:42:23.980 align:middle line:84%
I never get bored
looking at these things.

00:42:23.980 --> 00:42:25.800 align:middle line:84%
And I've taken
people on tours there

00:42:25.800 --> 00:42:27.550 align:middle line:84%
and it's hard to peel
them off the stones.

00:42:27.550 --> 00:42:29.230 align:middle line:84%
They literally become
part of the stone.

00:42:29.230 --> 00:42:31.480 align:middle line:84%
And I've watched them change,
literally, within a week

00:42:31.480 --> 00:42:33.313 align:middle line:84%
and they become completely
different people.

00:42:33.313 --> 00:42:34.690 align:middle line:84%
It's like they
recognize who they

00:42:34.690 --> 00:42:36.460 align:middle line:84%
are, what they're
doing here, but it's

00:42:36.460 --> 00:42:37.870 align:middle line:90%
a very personal journey.

00:42:37.870 --> 00:42:41.813 align:middle line:84%
It's though-- and my advice is,
go in there expecting nothing.

00:42:41.813 --> 00:42:43.730 align:middle line:84%
If you go there expecting
something to happen,

00:42:43.730 --> 00:42:44.530 align:middle line:90%
it won't happen.

00:42:44.530 --> 00:42:46.810 align:middle line:84%
Go in there with an open
mind and ask a question.

00:42:46.810 --> 00:42:50.110 align:middle line:84%
For example, my usual one
is, what's this really about?

00:42:50.110 --> 00:42:52.480 align:middle line:84%
Because my purpose is to
be a teacher to others.

00:42:52.480 --> 00:42:55.330 align:middle line:84%
I have to know my trade in
order to be a good teacher

00:42:55.330 --> 00:42:56.330 align:middle line:90%
to somebody else.

00:42:56.330 --> 00:42:58.480 align:middle line:84%
So I just say,
what is this about?

00:42:58.480 --> 00:43:00.430 align:middle line:84%
And then, there'll
be one stone that--

00:43:00.430 --> 00:43:03.040 align:middle line:84%
like all of them, they'll just
stand out and they'll say,

00:43:03.040 --> 00:43:03.850 align:middle line:90%
"come over here."

00:43:03.850 --> 00:43:04.940 align:middle line:90%
And I'll go, really?

00:43:04.940 --> 00:43:05.740 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Freddy.

00:43:05.740 --> 00:43:07.630 align:middle line:90%
>>SILVA: And I go, Freddy.

00:43:07.630 --> 00:43:09.340 align:middle line:84%
I'm not sure they
even know my name.

00:43:09.340 --> 00:43:10.510 align:middle line:90%
And I'll go and stand there.

00:43:10.510 --> 00:43:12.640 align:middle line:90%
I just put my back to the stone.

00:43:12.640 --> 00:43:14.918 align:middle line:84%
And before I realize it,
an hour's disappeared.

00:43:14.918 --> 00:43:16.960 align:middle line:84%
I think that I've been
standing next to the stone

00:43:16.960 --> 00:43:18.400 align:middle line:90%
for five seconds.

00:43:18.400 --> 00:43:20.998 align:middle line:84%
And then, I'm just
writing everything down.

00:43:20.998 --> 00:43:22.790 align:middle line:84%
I thought, this is
really incredible stuff.

00:43:22.790 --> 00:43:24.920 align:middle line:84%
And it leads on to
another year of research.

00:43:24.920 --> 00:43:28.210 align:middle line:84%
I mean, it's a great location
in which to really just download

00:43:28.210 --> 00:43:29.050 align:middle line:90%
information.

00:43:29.050 --> 00:43:30.938 align:middle line:84%
And you don't even
have to believe it.

00:43:30.938 --> 00:43:32.480 align:middle line:84%
I don't want anybody
to believe this.

00:43:32.480 --> 00:43:35.740 align:middle line:84%
I want to go and experience it
for yourself because this is

00:43:35.740 --> 00:43:38.410 align:middle line:84%
why the places were built.
And there's one in Lewis that

00:43:38.410 --> 00:43:42.400 align:middle line:84%
I'm very specific about
called [NON-ENGLISH]..

00:43:42.400 --> 00:43:46.630 align:middle line:84%
It's original name in Armenian
means "the place of seeing."

00:43:46.630 --> 00:43:48.297 align:middle line:84%
And it's the most
important stone circle

00:43:48.297 --> 00:43:50.755 align:middle line:84%
in the whole island and that's
where the priests used to go

00:43:50.755 --> 00:43:52.115 align:middle line:90%
to do their vision quests.

00:43:52.115 --> 00:43:53.740 align:middle line:84%
And that's why they
gave it their name.

00:43:53.740 --> 00:43:54.460 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Magical.

00:43:54.460 --> 00:43:56.080 align:middle line:84%
>>SILVA: And that's why
you go to these places,

00:43:56.080 --> 00:43:58.000 align:middle line:84%
to have this
interdimensional experience.

00:43:58.000 --> 00:44:00.550 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Freddy, where can
people see your documentary

00:44:00.550 --> 00:44:01.840 align:middle line:90%
and get your books?

00:44:01.840 --> 00:44:03.430 align:middle line:84%
>>SILVA: Well, they
can go on "Gaia."

00:44:03.430 --> 00:44:04.900 align:middle line:10%
They can go on my website--

00:44:04.900 --> 00:44:09.640 align:middle line:10%
invisibletemple.com-- and you'll
be there for a long, long time.

00:44:09.640 --> 00:44:12.340 align:middle line:84%
Eight books, 14
documentaries, and there's

00:44:12.340 --> 00:44:14.080 align:middle line:84%
another one in the
pipeline somewhere.

00:44:14.080 --> 00:44:15.580 align:middle line:90%
Never a boring moment.

00:44:15.580 --> 00:44:18.490 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: How would you rate
that area of Sardinia compared

00:44:18.490 --> 00:44:21.030 align:middle line:90%
to other places on the planet?

00:44:21.030 --> 00:44:21.830 align:middle line:10%
>>SILVA: Original.

00:44:21.830 --> 00:44:23.260 align:middle line:10%
They're all completely original.

00:44:23.260 --> 00:44:25.810 align:middle line:10%
Sardinia stands up by
itself because it's

00:44:25.810 --> 00:44:27.790 align:middle line:10%
one of the highest
concentrations of the most

00:44:27.790 --> 00:44:30.200 align:middle line:10%
ancient DNA in the
whole of Europe.

00:44:30.200 --> 00:44:34.180 align:middle line:84%
And its connections to
Armenia extend the story

00:44:34.180 --> 00:44:36.610 align:middle line:84%
even further back
into pre-history.

00:44:36.610 --> 00:44:39.940 align:middle line:84%
So it's part of another
developing, eye-opening series

00:44:39.940 --> 00:44:41.830 align:middle line:84%
in this quest to
try and find out

00:44:41.830 --> 00:44:43.060 align:middle line:90%
what the ancients were up to.

00:44:43.060 --> 00:44:43.540 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Super.

00:44:43.540 --> 00:44:45.373 align:middle line:84%
Freddy, thanks for being
on "Beyond Belief."

00:44:45.373 --> 00:44:46.645 align:middle line:90%
>>SILVA: Always a pleasure.

00:44:46.645 --> 00:44:49.480 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: These mystical
areas are truly remarkable.

00:44:49.480 --> 00:44:51.940 align:middle line:10%
Much more than one
would ever expect.

00:44:51.940 --> 00:44:55.810 align:middle line:10%
I'm George Noory, and thanks
for watching Beyond Belief."

